  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0202a3095b7477a4091d56344f0af6b3, type: 3}
  m_Name: AmericanMasculinityR2Graph
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp-Editor::DS.Data.Save.DSGraphSaveDataSO
  <FileName>k__BackingField: AmericanMasculinityR2
  <Groups>k__BackingField: []
  <DialogueNodes>k__BackingField:
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 1aac069a-0862-4f18-8583-f6fd7916220a
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName5
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: df202fea-3ef1-468d-b2ba-bba2d928ca0f
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 3008, y: 84}
    <Text>k__BackingField: But as economic pressure grows, here's where things become
      more complex. In her book "The Hearts of Men" by Barbara Ehrenreich, she raised
      an interesting point that there was an increasing number of men walking out
      of this traditional role of being a breadwinner.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 79439ec6-af00-47a6-8827-69b73fd0a424
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName10
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: d9a5de60-66ae-407a-af07-fc45cf4b111b
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 6576, y: 166.40001}
    <Text>k__BackingField: "Playboy also led to the Playboy philosophy. They also
      capitalise on society\u2019s perception that a man not settling down was a
      loser, but is also perceived as being a homosexual."
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: d9a5de60-66ae-407a-af07-fc45cf4b111b
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName11
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: db88dc27-7ba6-4c90-8d50-7f4618a419e2
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 7280.8, y: 180}
    <Text>k__BackingField: 'It argued that men who adopt the Playboy lifestyle, where
      they sleep around with many naked women, are not gay, but rather, they are
      too busy enjoying their heterosexuality.

'
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: db88dc27-7ba6-4c90-8d50-7f4618a419e2
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName12
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 4de2c6e8-80c5-4645-a877-d086c9cbe84b
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 7965.6, y: 180}
    <Text>k__BackingField: In some sense, Playboy became a business that sought to
      exploit the growing insecurity of men brought about by traditional social roles
      for a quick buck.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 4de2c6e8-80c5-4645-a877-d086c9cbe84b
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName13
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 15b3d14e-a55b-4dae-916b-7a93da25bbba
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 8707.2, y: 180}
    <Text>k__BackingField: The eventual outcome was that men began to rebel against
      the traditional role, either because they realised that growing economic pressure
      would drive them to their death, or because certain institutions began appearing
      in the market to exploit their own insecurity and promised that they would
      lead a much better life if they avoided adhering to traditional social roles.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 15b3d14e-a55b-4dae-916b-7a93da25bbba
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName14
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: bf5b2612-f8ad-4920-973d-f28db700aa66
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 9440, y: 202.40001}
    <Text>k__BackingField: 'Now, in order for this role to gradually change hands,
      women needed to get a job. '
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: bf5b2612-f8ad-4920-973d-f28db700aa66
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName15
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 3705404a-cc7c-4296-8f4a-a8c2dea8ca6a
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 10033.6, y: 202.40001}
    <Text>k__BackingField: "The logic was: \"If I don't want to work or I want to
      work less, then I need a woman to work to support us\u201D. And for a Playboy:
      \u201C I wanted you because you are well off to support me, or because you
      are going to get a well-paying job\"."
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 75c6f65b-4588-4edc-a312-d97c9fe58fd8
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName4
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 1aac069a-0862-4f18-8583-f6fd7916220a
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 2289.6, y: 84}
    <Text>k__BackingField: In America, there has always been, and is still, a longstanding
      culture that men were supposed to be the breadwinners of the family. They are
      pressured to start working young and get a good job to raise their family.
      In fact, non-married or unemployed men were seen as immature and viewed unfavourably
      by society..
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: ec556a63-3a6a-44c6-bb57-ce0602c41707
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName17
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 83271b25-8829-4c72-b514-81f97cd088e7
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 11459.2, y: 228}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Some men decided to ally with feminist movements. They
      began to adopt a less authoritative and softer behaviour, and started to support
      such movements precisely to achieve their agenda.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 83271b25-8829-4c72-b514-81f97cd088e7
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName18
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: c9cb79f9-95c5-46d8-afd7-25b38679c48d
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 12228.8, y: 228}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Indeed, this was one of the main critiques in Barbara's
      book. She reported that men sought women's liberation to extract these benefits
      of feminism.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: d5132a37-36f1-4e46-a971-ce07d3999670
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName3
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 75c6f65b-4588-4edc-a312-d97c9fe58fd8
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 1537.6, y: 64.799995}
    <Text>k__BackingField: To understand this, we need to first recognise the gender
      role of men in America.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: d4ce026e-1625-41ea-9e6c-7e4dc07edb22
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: d5132a37-36f1-4e46-a971-ce07d3999670
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 756.8, y: 64.799995}
    <Text>k__BackingField: The second reason is an interesting one, which argues
      that men adopt a gentler form of masculinity to ensure the success of feminism
      because growing economic pressures lead to a growing number of men rejecting
      the traditional role.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: df202fea-3ef1-468d-b2ba-bba2d928ca0f
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName6
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: ae08ac04-b0c3-4cf6-be83-2adad61a2ede
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 3703.2, y: 84}
    <Text>k__BackingField: 'She explained that to cope with rising costs, men threw
      themselves deeper into their work, with some dying in the process. Heart failure
      was one of the leading causes of death for white-collar male Americans back
      then due to stress from working too much.

'
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 9f50c5c0-298a-4574-9205-ba7d599bc71b
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName9
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 79439ec6-af00-47a6-8827-69b73fd0a424
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 5856, y: 124.799995}
    <Text>k__BackingField: 'To further capitalise on this feeling of resentment,
      Barbara cited that this was also the time when institutions like Playboy started
      to emerge to cater to this growing audience of dissatisfied men, which further
      fanned the flames of resentment by portraying bachelorhood as being able to
      "enjoy the finer things in life". '
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: ae08ac04-b0c3-4cf6-be83-2adad61a2ede
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName7
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 9f50c5c0-298a-4574-9205-ba7d599bc71b
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 4889.6, y: 150.40001}
    <Text>k__BackingField: The growing economic pressure drove men to become increasingly
      resentful of the traditional role thrusted on them.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 3705404a-cc7c-4296-8f4a-a8c2dea8ca6a
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName16
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: ec556a63-3a6a-44c6-bb57-ce0602c41707
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 10736.8, y: 228}
    <Text>k__BackingField: And what better way for this to be realised than through
      the second wave of feminism, which sought to encourage more women to work as
      a way to liberate themselves.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: c9cb79f9-95c5-46d8-afd7-25b38679c48d
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName19
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 5d551bc7-94ff-4eff-b36c-a51ae973a40f
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 12925.6, y: 211.20001}
    <Text>k__BackingField: On the other hand, to the hungry capitalist, more women
      working also meant the economy would grow, and more money could be made.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: e5384309-e31a-4821-86fb-3ee3fe58a2ee
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName21
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: b0ca13bf-3131-4039-af4a-8c90d35aac72
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 14364, y: 211.20001}
    <Text>k__BackingField: The capitalists knew that this was considered unpaid labour,
      so they wanted more women to join the workforce to contribute to the economy,
      which obviously means they earn more money. At the same time, having women
      working meant they can have their own income to spend more on goods and services,
      thereby adding more people to the customer base.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 5d551bc7-94ff-4eff-b36c-a51ae973a40f
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName20
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: e5384309-e31a-4821-86fb-3ee3fe58a2ee
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 13662.4, y: 211.20001}
    <Text>k__BackingField: This is not entirely surprising, as women back then were
      confined to being homemakers to raise their families.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 4657604687955570395, guid: 594dd21517fbf9a419c445a95d896f89, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: b0ca13bf-3131-4039-af4a-8c90d35aac72
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName22
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 15062.4, y: 211.20001}
    <Text>k__BackingField: As a result, capitalists also pushed for the success of
      the feminist movement by espousing liberal values like equality and attempts
      to normalise a less authoritarian and more liberal form of masculinity for
